data.description: This beautiful 2-bedroom home features a great layout! Enjoy the sunshine coming through the bay window in the spacious living room, beautiful french doors in the dining area, a large deck out back overlooking the yard, and some really nice updates including a new roof Oct. 2020 and new furnace 2021. Call me to schedule a showing today!
